refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public mixedpht\Vector::pop
This method pops a value from the end of a vector (in constant time). Popping a value from an empty vector will result in an Error exception.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Popping a value from a vector


<?php

use pht\Vector;

$vector = new Vector();

$vector->push(1);
$vector[] = 2;

var_dump($vector->pop());


    &example.outputs;


int(2)
